<HEAD>CHAP. VI.</HEAD>
<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><L>"I care not, Fortune! what you me deny;</L>
<L>You cannot rob me of free nature's grace;</L>
<L>You cannot &s;hut the windows of the &s;ky,</L>
