<P>Madame Montoni's &s;ufferings, at length, ro&s;e above her pride, and when Emily had before entered the room, &s;he would have told them <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> not her hu&s;band prevented her; now that &s;he was no longer re&s;trained by his pre&s;ence, &s;he poured forth all her complaints to her niece.</P>
